From: Marcin Serwin <marcin@serwin.dev>
Date: Thu, 21 Aug 2025 03:47:45 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Update imagemin-pngquant to the newest version

I was trying to use pngquant 3 for generating icons, however, the
imagemin-pngquant version was too old and was generating garbage.
Bumping it to the newest version resolved the issue.

Signed-off-by: Marcin Serwin <marcin@serwin.dev>
